text: Hossein Rahmati (, born March 21, 1994) is an Iranian professional basketball player.Hossein Rahmati FIBA.com He currently plays for Fryshuset in the Swedish Basketball League as well as for the Iranian national basketball team, as a Power Forward.2014 FIBA Asia Cup FIBA Archive He is 6'8" in height.Asia Basket Profile Asia Basket He was a member of the Iran national youth team.
